In 2016 KORE achieved position as the 4th highest vendor in "Ability to Execute" in the 2016 Gartner Magic Quadrant for managed machine-to-machine services, worldwide.
With a deep, rich suite of IoT and M2M network services, KORE offers true global connectivity, with high-quality integration solutions for customers from all industries. In partnership with our leading multi-national cellular and satellite carrier partners, we offer the best natively-provisioned global connectivity in the market place, including GSM, CDMA and satellite services.
 
When you partner with KORE, you’re guaranteed:

Access to the largest, more comprehensive global network service footprint
Assistance from a dedicated team of IoT and M2M industry experts
Optimized GSM SIM option delivering to more than 180 countries worldwide
Ability to manage all devices with real-time network visibility
Multiple, redundant connections between KORE and our carrier partners’ networks
A consultative partnership to help you get to market quickly and effectively
One comprehensive business management platform to consolidate all services and billing
Ability to activate on-demand with no minimum service period or per-device contract

 
Gain access to our exclusively-designed IoT and M2M optimized network today! Contact our team by filling out the form to the right or call (877) 710-5673  – you’ll speak to an expert dedicated to IoT and M2M services delivery excellence.































































































































The Largest, Most Comprehensive Global Network Service Footprint
Including LTE, GSM and CDMA and via our partnership with Iridium, truly global satellite connectivity is achieved via a single – or dual for redundancy and fail-over – connection between KORE and its customers.



















A Partnership Approach
At KORE, we do not believe in competing with our customers. That is why we only supply network services - not hardware or applications/solutions to the market.



















A Dedicated Team of Experts
KORE's experienced team of client managers and support technicians help get customers to market quickly and effectively. KORE has distinguished itself in terms of our customer and technical support, providing service level metrics including a technical escalation process for expiditing and resolving all service delivery related issues.















































